commit.message:
gcc_update: libjava/configure.ac -> configure.in.

2004-08-04  Paolo Bonzini  <gcc@gcc.gnu.org>

	* gcc_update: libjava/configure.ac -> configure.in.  Automake
	1.4 does not handle configure.ac properly.

From-SVN: r85556
